# Session Lore Spec

## Purpose
Create callback humor that feels personal and funny without becoming creepy.

## Phase 1
No session lore logic in core gameplay yet beyond keeping architecture ready.

## Later tracked examples
- brokeFirstCount
- peakAura
- earlyReleaseCount
- perfectReleaseCount
- almostHadItCount
- sabotageCount
- comebackCount
- quietWinCount

## Uses
- round-end labels
- mini summaries
- crowd bias
- spectator-facing callouts

## Rules
- session-based at first
- gameplay-relevant only
- never overlong
- easy to disable
- no invasive personal storage